<section class="safe-space-section section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="safe-space-content reveal">
            <span class="section-label">Your Safe Space</span>
            <h2>Thinking about starting a business?<br><em>The right knowledge is your foundation.</em></h2>
            
            <p class="lead-text">
                Whether you're just starting out or looking to scale, you need a safe space to find reliable answers. We don't just offer theoretical advice; we share real, practical business experiences. 
            </p>
            
            <div class="benefits-grid">
                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon">
                        <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.75"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4>Accounting & Compliance</h4>
                    <p>Substantive accounting support to safely guide you through regulations and taxes without the jargon.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon">
                        <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.75"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4>Branding Strategy</h4>
                    <p>Help in developing a strong brand identity that resonates and sets you apart in the market.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon">
                        <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.75"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4>Actionable Checklists</h4>
                    <p>Practical, step-by-step checklists to keep your business organized, compliant, and growing.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
.safe-space-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: #f8fafc; /* light gray/blue tint */
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--navy);
    background: #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.safe-space-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
}

.safe-space-content h2 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--accent);
}

.lead-text {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--navy-mid);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
}

.benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
}

.benefit-card {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(15,39,68,.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.benefit-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15,39,68,.08);
}

.benefit-icon {
    width: 3.5rem;
    height: 3.5rem;
    background: #f0f9ff;
    color: var(--accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.benefit-icon svg {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
}

.benefit-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--navy);
}

.benefit-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
}
</style>
